des:
Listen to this story about the super wall and the anomalous multiverse, straight out of unofficial marvel comics. A must have story about being a transporter, watch how Beeram, a transporter of the drunken folk, hits a time anomaly from a neighboring time-line, listen on to how he take the help of retired unofficial NASA staff to return his kid to his timeline!
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
